data.description: Welcome to your charming Cape Cod oasis in coveted Colonial Place! This delightful 4-bedroom, 2-full bath residence boasts a timeless appeal and modern convenience. Step inside to discover an inviting open concept, great for both relaxation and entertainment. With 2 bedrooms upstairs and 2 down, this home offers flexibility and space for all your needs. Embrace outdoor living w/ stunning landscaping that frames the property. Plus, enjoy the convenience of a detached garage for all your storage needs. Nestled just a few blocks from the serene Elizabeth River, this location offers the best of coastal living while still being near urban amenities. Colonial Place has beautiful walking trails, dog park, kids park, & active Civic League w/ community events. Enjoy historical charm & modern amenities. Home is selling as-is.
